Executive Summary
The core library is solid and well-architected — clean facade pattern, proper DI, OWASP ASVS Level 2/3 security hardening, and 80.14% test coverage across 270 tests. The main weaknesses are: (1) test quality gaps (error paths, concurrency, Postgres), (2) missing launch infrastructure (CI/CD, linting, docs), and (3) a few production hardening issues (broad exception catching, no pattern quota).

